                    </div>
                    <span>If you want to learn Direct3D programming. Use this book. It helps you step by step to learn the most important things first to be able understand the more experienced stuff later.<BR>This is the book for starters everyone has waiting for.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A beginner opinion</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
